# Vantage v0.5.6 *Prerelease*

## **Additions:**

 - Added 3 new operator preview modes:

	- Max (Shows current, previous and next of all content shown)
	- Full (Previous version used in all old releases)
	- Minimized (Shows the bare minimum of content)
	- Hidden (Hides preview entirely)

 - Allowed videos to be set as idle backgrounds 
 - Added NKJV and NIV to
   Bible versions
   

 - Added 'sandbox' mode which allows user to preview songs before sending to show screen. *Broken.*
 ## Bugfixes:
 

 - Fixed crashing on capslock bug for MacOS
 - Fixed items not contrasting well when switching themes
 - Fixed low resolution bug with Youtube videos
 - Fixed window not fitting in screen in high DPI resolutions
 

